<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Teamwork Commerce has partnered with ShippyPro, a global shipping platform that helps businesses automate shipping, tracking, and returns while optimizing delivery costs. The partnership lets retailers manage order fulfilment and returns directly through Teamwork Commerce's Mobile Point of Sale application.</p>

<h2>How the integration works</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">ShippyPro is a shipping hub that helps merchants ship, track, and return in-store, store-to-store, and e-commerce orders from one place. Integrated directly into Teamwork Commerce's Mobile POS, retailers can create labels, cut processing times, and keep order fulfilment accurate and consistent. ShippyPro Optimizer also gives retailers visibility into shipping KPIs, so they can track delivery performance and costs.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Once a shipping label is generated and printed within the POS, it updates automatically in Teamwork's Order Management System, keeping data accurate across channels. Retailers can configure advanced settings, including available shipping methods, restrictions, and automated workflows such as generating return labels when needed.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Carrier management is streamlined as well: available services are populated automatically based on each carrier's fulfilment capabilities, covering Ground, Economy, Next Day, Express, and Standard delivery. The integration supports shipping methods across the US, Canada, UK, Europe, and Mexico, with access to a full list of 171 options from one centralized database.</p>

<h2>In their words</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Francesco Borghi, CEO and founder of ShippyPro, said: "Our mission is to build the logistics infrastructure for global commerce, empowering brands to operate smarter and deliver the best possible experiences through fulfillment. Our partnership with Teamwork Commerce allows retailers to strengthen their omnichannel offering from their POS, with full visibility on shipping KPIs to reduce delivery costs, improve carrier performance, and grow the brand globally."</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Amber Hovious, VP of Marketing and Partnerships at Teamwork Commerce, said: "This partnership allows retailers to significantly and seamlessly enhance their fulfilment capabilities, ensuring reliable operations that deliver long-term success. This enables retailers to streamline their logistics and optimize costs, all while creating high-quality experiences for consumers."</p>
